00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:41,080
Boss, please sign this.

699
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:46,600
The person in charge of each project.

700
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:48,400
Go to the conference room in five minutes

701
00:33:48,560 --> 00:33:49,720
