781
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,480
It's all my mistake.

782
00:38:55,680 --> 00:38:57,120
I was too harsh.

783
00:38:58,240 --> 00:38:59,760
You can lead the team

784
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:01,360
