794
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:23,200
By the way,

795
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:25,120
Xiao Ning is still waiting for you outside.

796
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:26,720
Did you...

797
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:29,560
