snacks with friends now.

798
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,800
I'm late already.

799
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:31,880
Well, I'll get going.

800
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:33,240
Lock the door and windows

801
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:33,960
