802
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:06,240
Brother Dong.

803
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:07,160
Xiao Ning.

804
00:40:07,160 --> 00:40:08,080
You've finished working?

805
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,480
